OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Millions of people face the dilemma of 
OL,6, cutting spending on food and clothing  
OL,7, to pay their energy bill, one          
OL,8, supplier's boss has said.              
OL,10,FBill Bullen, chief executive of Utilita
OL,11,F- which serves prepayment meter        
OL,12,Fcustomers - said government financial  
OL,13,Fsupport was not directed sufficiently  
OL,14,Fto those who needed it most.           
OL,16,FHe said ministers should spend money on
OL,17,F"insulating the hell out of Britain".  
OL,19,FThere are growing calls for help on    
OL,20,Fbills ahead of the Spring Statement.   
